<para>Shows the dialog, returning one of wxID_OK, wxID_CANCEL, wxID_YES, wxID_NO. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classwx_rich_message_dialog_1a6c2650439d36a09ee3292896861a5a16" kindref="member">IsCheckBoxChecked()</ref> can be called afterwards to retrieve the value of the check box if one was used. </para>
